## [Unreleased]

### Added
- New dark mode toggle to the user settings dashboard.
- Automatic session timeout alert after 15 minutes of inactivity.

### Fixed
- Memory leak issue causing high CPU usage during large data CSV exports.

## - 2026-06-15

### Added
- Integration with external payment gateways for global currencies.
- Multilingual support for Spanish, French, and Japanese languages.

### Changed
- Refactored the core authentication middleware to improve loading speed by 20%.
- Updated the primary font family to enhance accessibility and UI readability.

### Deprecated
- The legacy `/api/v1/old-auth` endpoint will be removed in version 2.0.0.

### Removed
- Removed the deprecated background synchronization service tool.

## - 2026-03-22

### Fixed
- Broken profile picture upload button on mobile Safari browsers.
- Spelling error inside the welcome email notification template.

### Security
- Patched cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability found in the comments input section.

## - 2026-01-10

### Added
- Initial public release of the responsive web application dashboard.
- User account creation, profile management, and password recovery systems.

